adObject` paths, including the remaining `writeObject`/`readObject` call sites.\n\n- Updated `tests/src/org.scala-lang/scala-library/2.11.8/src/test/resources/META-INF/native-image/reachability-metadata.json`\n  - Added Native Image test metadata for:\n    - `scala.collection.immutable.LazyList`\n    - `scala.collection.immutable.LazyList$SerializationProxy`\n    - `scala.collection.immutable.LazyList$State$Empty$`\n    - `scala.collection.generic.SerializeEnd$`\n\nI did not compile or run the tests, per instruction.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0e744e74d944971c0169f51f9730f081a2a6cb5f88ab241d62\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 959, "output": 944, "cacheRead": 33280, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 35183, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1777672074391, "responseId": "resp_0e744e74d944971c0169f51f8ad2e081a291ada64ab14b9998"}}
